        <abstract>
            <p>Does not think WRG’s theory [about ridges of skin on palm and finger-ends?] will hold.</p>
            <p>Does not believe the beard in monkeys and goats could be protective like the lion’s mane.</p>
            <p>Thanks him for fact about setters.</p>
            <p>Is perplexed about the reported milk secretion in pubescent boys.</p>
        </abstract>
